    "name": "Sorcery Slam",
    "steam_appid": 3276960,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276960/extras/4221357fe56c4aaf2e09e6dd9795be8d.avif?t=1764919492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276960/extras_big/4221357fe56c4aaf2e09e6dd9795be8d.avif?t=1764919492 width=800 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get your block in position and place it instantly with the SLAM button! Save a block or item for a more opportune time with the bank button!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276960/extras/eef7895d6011c2a296c0d1a68c98c68a.avif?t=1764919492\" width=1302 height=208 /></span>Play multiplayer online with adjustable difficulty so anyone has a chance to win! Owners of the game can host a match that their friends can join from the Demo completely free!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276960/extras/b399e2a1b57a3d5fa11f0297393e40ed.avif?t=1764919492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276960/extras_big/b399e2a1b57a3d5fa11f0297393e40ed.avif?t=1764919492 width=800 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clear more than one line with a single block to clutter your opponents with hexes! Larger combos cause stronger attacks, and complete in real time! Begin your next move immediately with fast paced puzzling action!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276960/extras/48f7e11320216d4fe0c0cc513ba3f0db.avif?t=1764919492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276960/extras_big/48f7e11320216d4fe0c0cc513ba3f0db.avif?t=1764919492 width=800 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add to your power meter with long lines, combos and clear streaks for a random item to pave your winning path. Get more powerful items when you’re behind to close the distance to your goal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276960/extras/78f3a9f2e513264fa4eb027859727080.avif?t=1764919492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276960/extras_big/78f3a9f2e513264fa4eb027859727080.avif?t=1764919492 width=800 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjust your difficulty to raise the bar for powerful enchanters and lower it for humble apprentices. Tune your experience for your group and everyone has a chance to win! Choose your colors and customize clothes to create your perfect sorcerer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276960/extras/26375a9563f83f372a052694bacfc026.avif?t=1764919492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276960/extras_big/26375a9563f83f372a052694bacfc026.avif?t=1764919492 width=800 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sprint</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beat each level in succession as fast as you can and go for your best time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay alive as long as possible before the Gems advance and more and more frequent intervals! Get combos to slow down their advance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
